c.
<html>
    <body>
        <p>
            <h1 align="center">HTML</h1>
            <h3>HTML stands for Hyper Text Markup Language</h3>
            <h4>HTML is the standard markup language for creating
            Web pages.HTML describes the structure of a Web page.
            HTML consists of a series of elements.HTML elements 
            tell the browser how to display the content.</h4>
    </body>
</html>

